I was hoping to see the benchmark improve but it seems it doesn't but it decreases a bit after the optimizations of this PR.

Benched on M2 Pro

On 21a184db63bd13cf0c2dff9e6e61ca85f2ff4454
|               ns/op |                op/s |    err% |     total | benchmark
|--------------------:|--------------------:|--------:|----------:|:----------
