On 12760a57b3a6cd1aeb3b7532311f648de2b45aa4

|               ns/op |                op/s |    err% |     total | benchmark
|--------------------:|--------------------:|--------:|----------:|:----------
|          152,479.17 |            6,558.27 |    1.3% |      0.01 | `Linearize16TxWorstCase120Iters`
